{"tid":1284474,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[拘留記] 我 冇野講 困兩天相對望 在臭格中講肚餓 犬隻還如常扮惡","createTime":"2019-07-04T07:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T12:05:11.000Z","uid":86723,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"39b7d4864363bca206bddeb28b4edceb097e72e5","tid":1284474,"uid":86723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T07:41:21.000Z","msg":"手機我<br />\n已上鎖<br />\n你顯得很錯愕<br />\n閒時驗傷中過 零動作<br />\n被塔都可齋坐"},{"pid":"b346fb03473699c1559da280d702be5aa66a6bc6","tid":1284474,"uid":86723,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T07:48:07.000Z","msg":"你冇食藥 還是吃錯<br />\n我冇罪還塔我<br />\n做個起底員 卻因私隱被鎖<br />\n<br />\n要叫大狀 頑強對抗<br />\n冷氣大唔太妥<br />\n再叫警犬給氈我<br />\n有三急廁所中過<br />\n又非遣返中國"},{"pid":"c5cc29054a5e85b92fe61e856bf28a4f5b5ce1f7","tid":1284474,"uid":86723,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T11:53:42.000Z","msg":"我  冇野講<br />\n被困兩天終拍岸<br />\n如無罪怎需反駁<br />\n胡鬧夠  冇證物敢兇我<br />\n<br />\n不知道  不知道  我也不知道<br />\n搜身過  遭質我  簽紙喎  想屈我<br />\n連日地  狂被你  追擊 追擊  追擊<br />\n為何被  追擊  衰得佢  想屈我"},{"pid":"ed56aad15b134dca4277b8034cd4da691ef5827a","tid":1284474,"uid":86723,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T13:08:38.000Z","msg":"你冇食藥 還是吃錯<br />\n這控罪無答案<br />\n做個起底員<br />\n卻因私隱被鎖<br />\n<br />\n要叫大狀  頑強對抗<br />\n控訴為何成案<br />\n若夾硬說起底錯<br />\n一秒後捕捉歸案  動火"},{"pid":"0f9dc9b82c5b35b9cfc90a2c74514524b44606b5","tid":1284474,"uid":86723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:20:17.000Z","msg":"我 冇野講<br />\n困兩天都快樂<br />\n靈魂尚於軀殼<br />\n仇敵已 賣了身 給中國<br />\n全毅進  我祝你  長壽到  被遺返  番中國"},{"pid":"ac7b36dcd4789456174a33e94c82d2411afc254e","tid":1284474,"uid":86723,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:22:33.000Z","msg":"原曲 : 失魂記<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qHQ5QcqhsnQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqHQ5QcqhsnQ&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFI1EyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=558f0ec7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qHQ5QcqhsnQ</a><br />\n<br />\n我 冇野講<br />\n困兩天相對望<br />\n在臭格中講肚餓<br />\n犬隻還如常扮惡<br />\n<br />\n手機我 已上鎖<br />\n你顯得很錯愕<br />\n閒時驗傷中過  零動作<br />\n被塔都可齋坐<br />\n<br />\n你冇食藥 還是吃錯<br />\n我冇罪還塔我<br />\n做個起底員 卻因私隱被鎖<br />\n<br />\n要叫大狀 頑強對抗<br />\n冷氣大唔太妥<br />\n再叫警犬給氈我<br />\n有三急廁所中過<br />\n又非遣返中國<br />\n<br />\n我  冇野講<br />\n被困兩天終拍岸<br />\n如無罪怎需反駁<br />\n胡鬧夠  冇證物敢兇我<br />\n<br />\n不知道  不知道  我也不知道<br />\n搜身過  遭質我  簽紙喎  想屈我<br />\n連日地  狂被你  追擊 追擊  追擊<br />\n為何被  追擊  衰得佢  想屈我<br />\n<br />\n你冇食藥 還是吃錯<br />\n我冇罪還塔我<br />\n做個起底員<br />\n卻因私隱被鎖<br />\n<br />\n要叫大狀  頑強對抗<br />\n控訴為何成案<br />\n若夾硬說起底錯<br />\n一秒後捕捉歸案  動火<br />\n<br />\n我 冇野講<br />\n困兩天都快樂<br />\n靈魂尚於軀殼<br />\n仇敵已 賣了身 給中國<br />\n全毅進  我祝你  長壽到  被遺返  番中國"},{"pid":"5ff6becc90c3bf666369c7785fafc0304291f0b4","tid":1284474,"uid":271123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:23:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f99cdd1dc609110168a384143b07f4dd3a83878","tid":1284474,"uid":60952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:27:22.000Z","msg":"唱咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e248948cec0833b70170da93646f6587b4303c4","tid":1284474,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:52:56.000Z","msg":"搵人唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744e1968f92642b8460482c2187a944d99c547b7","tid":1284474,"uid":86723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f99cdd1dc609110168a384143b07f4dd3a83878","tid":1284474,"uid":60952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:27:22.000Z","msg":"唱咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:23:51.000Z","msg":"睇標題都唱到咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e83bbb8f7a632c54ea571893291fb66169c6560","tid":1284474,"uid":86723,"like":0,"dislike":0